title: Snaps - College Football Playoff predictions: Could Georgia, Alabama & Tennessee all get in?
itunes:title: Snaps - College Football Playoff predictions: Could Georgia, Alabama & Tennessee all get in?
description:
Aaron Murray and T-Bob Hebert discuss who would be in their College Football Playoff if the season ended today. Could Nick Saban's Alabama Crimson Tide, Kirby Smart's Georgia Bulldogs, and Josh Heupel's Tennessee Volunteers all get in? Later, the guys question if Steve Sarkisian is the right man for the Texas job and debate what the best Halloween CFB costume would be. #Volume #ColinCowherd #Herd
